.Sh DIAGNOSTICS
The
.Fn getipnodebyname
and
.Fn getipnodebyaddr
functions
returns
.Dv NULL
on errors.
The integer values pointed to by
.Fa error_num
may then be checked to see whether this is a temporary failure
or an invalid or unknown host.
The meanings of each error code are described in
.Xr gethostbyname 3 .
.\"
