.Sh BUGS
The
.Fn getipnodebyname
and
.Fn getipnodebyaddr
functions
do not handle scoped IPv6 address properly.
If you use these functions,
your program will not be able to handle scoped IPv6 addresses.
For IPv6 address manipulation,
.Fn getaddrinfo 3
and
.Fn getnameinfo 3
are recommended.
.Pp
